title: Live: Jays vs. Rangers, Game 4 | Blue Jays | Sports | Toronto Sun
text:
It's another elimination game for the Blue Jays this afternoon in Texas.
The Blue Jays trail the Rangers 2-1 in the best-of-five ALDS heading into Game 4. Knuckleballer R.A. Dickey gets the start for Toronto, which stayed alive with a 5-1 win in Texas on Sunday night.
Our team of baseball writers will offer their analysis throughout today's game in Arlington. ( Click here for a mobile-friendly link. )
